manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: 111 Makeup Brushes Show Your Beauty Create striking looks with specific brushes for concealer, foundation, eyeshadow, eyebrows, lips and more.

111-1 Brand 1 Team Makes 1 Product-Makeup Brushes 1 Set Meets All Your Makeup Needs Specialized, cruelty-free brushes for a luxurious feel and professional result Peachy pink and turquoise blue blended set，also suitable for little girls Soft and sumptuous microcrystalline fiber bristles Geometric handles for a comfortable grip（The surface is sprayed with rubber paint, which brings a high-level texture and a softer touch） Durable aluminum tube reduces bristle loss Stylish blue/pink color 4pcs face basic bigger face brushes 11pcs smaller eye brushes 3pcs sponge 1pc product description

This set meet nearly all your makeup needs,designed for professionals and beginner. It covers all areas on your face It works well for eyes,nose, lips,brow,cheeks,forehead and even hard-to-reach areas on your face. It is useful for versatile applications like Powder, Blush, Contour, Eye Shadow, Concealing, Blending, Nose Shading, Lip Lining, Eyebrow, Eyeliner, Lash,Contouring,Highlighting and more. Usage Use the blending brush to buff out harsh lines for a well-blended effect. Use the eyeshadow brush to place color evenly across the eyelid. Use the shader brush to apply color to precise areas of the eye or to smudge the lower lash line. Use the concealer brush to apply product with small strokes. Use the powder brush to apply product evenly on the face. Package contents: 1*15pcs Makeup Brush Set and 3pcs Sponge NOTE: The new brushes will have smells. It will disappear after washing or taking it out for a day.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality brush set that doesnʻt cost a lot!
reviews.reviewText: I have been using my 111 Pink Blue Gradient Makeup Brushes and Makeup Sponges Makeup Tool Set for some time and I have been very impressed by the quality and variety of the brushes and sponges. There are Several types of sponges for blending and contouring including in the set, as well as brushes for applying every type of makeup.The brushes are made of synthetic fibers that feel gentle on the skin and apply makeup smoothly and evenly. The handles are also sturdy and well-made, and the design is pink and blue gradient that goes perfect with my color aesthetic.The sponges included in the set are also very soft and blend my makeup seamlessly. The sponges are available in several shapes and sizes, so I can find the right sponge for each step of my makeup routine.111 Pink Blue Gradient Makeup Brushes and Makeup Sponges Makeup Tool Set is an excellent value for the price and the quality of the tools is a great investment for someone looking for a good quality makeup brush set without spending a lot of money.

reviews.reviewText: Nice amount of brushes and they are nice & soft. The handles are plastic but seem sturdy. My only complaint is I wish the packaging for these was giftable; It’s just a clear pack with all the brushes. I removed them and tried to come up with a creative way to put them into a gift but by themselves the packaging isn’t very giftable. Price is okay but over the holiday season I saw some sets that had prettier packaging for similar or less price.
